          Rue de l’Ecole-Supérieur 2<br />
          C.P. 5987<br />
          1002 Lausanne</p>
          <p>Tel: 021 312 44 70<br />Fax:	021 311 81 12</p>
          <%= link_to("Agrandir la carte","http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=%C3%A9cole+vinet+lausanne&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=69.476188,177.451172&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=%C3%A9cole+vinet&amp;hnear=Lausanne,+Vaud,+Switzerland&amp;cid=5096095572938173010&amp;ll=46.519894,6.637373&amp;spn=0.011812,0.018368&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A", {:onClick => "window.open(this.href,'_blank');return false;" } ) %>

